  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A streamlined and lightweight backpack unit, featuring an elegant single-thruster design. This exclusive exosuit augmentation commemorates completion of the inaugural <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>, 'Pioneers'.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装置套装外观</span>。<br><br>一款流线型轻量背包，优雅的单助推器设计是它的亮点。这款专属的套装外观纪念了你完成的第一次<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>設計簡化的輕量背包組，有著優雅的單一推進器設計。這個特殊強化套裝擴充紀念第一次完成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>「先鋒」。<br><br>能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變強化套裝的外觀。"
  },
